CMPML, Department of System Failure!

2D Game Engine including two full games!!!

1. Be on Windows.

2. Have Visual Studio installed.

3. Go to the directory GameEngine\GameLib and run :
	nmake all

4. Go to the directory GameEngine and run :
	nmake all

5. Go to the directory PSnakes and run :
	nmake all
	nmake install
	cd Binaries
	PSnakes.exe

6. Have fun with Physical Snakes!!!

7. Go to the top level directory and run :
	nmake all
	nmake install
	cd Binaries
	SchizoDriver.exe

8. Have fun with SchizoDriver!!!

9. The PSnakes code is best as a starting example for your own projects.

10. Create cool stuff ...

End of Document.